msgid "Content"
msgstr "Konten"

msgid "Image"
msgstr "Gambar"

msgid ""
"Optional image for modal display. Choose between banner (above content) or "
"background (behind text with overlay)."
msgstr ""
"Gambar opsional untuk tampilan modal. Pilih antara banner (di atas konten) "
"atau latar belakang (di belakang teks dengan lapisan)."

msgid "Link"
msgstr "Tautan"

msgid "Display"
msgstr "Tampilan"

msgid "Visibility Rules"
msgstr "Aturan Visibilitas"

msgid ""
"Optional: restrict when this announcement is shown based on advanced "
"conditions."
msgstr ""
"Opsional: batasi kapan pengumuman ini ditampilkan berdasarkan kondisi "
"lanjutan."

msgid "Title"
msgstr "Judul"

msgid "No expiry"
msgstr "Tidak ada masa berlaku"

msgid "Expired"
msgstr "Sudah Berakhir"

msgid "Active"
msgstr "Aktif"

msgid "Status"
msgstr "Status"

msgid "List active announcements"
msgstr "Daftar pengumuman aktif"

msgid ""
"Public endpoint. Returns all enabled, non-expired announcements ordered by "
"priority ascending, then created_at descending. Used by the storefront "
"announcement widget."
msgstr ""
"Titik akhir umum. Mengembalikan semua pengumuman yang aktif dan belum "
"kedaluwarsa, diurutkan berdasarkan prioritas secara ascending, kemudian "
"created_at secara descending. Digunakan oleh widget pengumuman toko online."

msgid "List of active announcements"
msgstr "Daftar pengumuman aktif"

msgid "Get announcement detail"
msgstr "Dapatkan detail pengumuman"

msgid ""
"Public endpoint. Returns full announcement data including body HTML, image "
"URL, and display mode for the storefront modal. Returns 404 if the "
"announcement is inactive, expired, or does not exist."
msgstr ""
"Titik akhir umum. Mengembalikan data pengumuman lengkap termasuk body HTML, "
"URL gambar, dan mode tampilan untuk modal toko online. Mengembalikan 404 "
"jika pengumuman tidak aktif, sudah kedaluwarsa, atau tidak ada."

msgid "Announcement primary key"
msgstr "Kunci utama pengumuman"

msgid "Announcement detail"
msgstr "Detail pengumuman"

msgid "Not found, inactive, or expired"
msgstr "Tidak ditemukan, tidak aktif, atau sudah kedaluwarsa"

msgid "Announcements"
msgstr "Pengumuman"

msgid "No Link"
msgstr "Tidak Ada Tautan"

msgid "Product"
msgstr "Produk"

msgid "Category"
msgstr "Kategori"

msgid "Blog Post"
msgstr "Posting Blog"

msgid "Page"
msgstr "Halaman"

msgid "Custom URL"
msgstr "URL Kustom"

msgid "Banner Image (above content)"
msgstr "Gambar Banner (di atas konten)"

msgid "Background Image (with overlay)"
msgstr "Gambar Latar Belakang (dengan lapisan)"

msgid "Announcement title - supports basic styling (bold, italic, color)"
msgstr "Judul pengumuman - mendukung gaya dasar (tebal, miring, warna)"

msgid "Optional detailed content for modal display"
msgstr "Konten rinci opsional untuk tampilan modal"

msgid "Optional image for modal display"
msgstr "Gambar opsional untuk tampilan modal"

msgid "How to display the image in the modal"
msgstr "Cara menampilkan gambar dalam modal"

msgid ""
"Overlay opacity when image is used as background (0 = transparent, 1 = "
"opaque)"
msgstr ""
"Ketebalan lapisan overlay ketika gambar digunakan sebagai latar belakang (0 "
"= transparan, 1 = tidak transparan)"

msgid "Type of link for this announcement"
msgstr "Jenis tautan untuk pengumuman ini"

msgid "Product to link to"
msgstr "Produk untuk dikaitkan"

msgid "Category to link to"
msgstr "Kategori untuk dikaitkan"

msgid "Blog post to link to"
msgstr "Posting blog untuk dikaitkan"

msgid "Page to link to"
msgstr "Halaman untuk dikaitkan"

msgid "Custom URL for the link"
msgstr "URL kustom untuk tautan"

msgid "Button text for modal link, e.g. \"Shop Now\""
msgstr "Teks tombol untuk tautan modal, contoh: \"Beli Sekarang\""

msgid ""
"If enabled, clicking the announcement opens a modal with full content. If "
"disabled, clicking navigates directly to the link URL."
msgstr ""
"Jika diaktifkan, mengklik pengumuman akan membuka modal dengan konten "
"lengkap. Jika dinonaktifkan, mengklik akan langsung mengarah ke URL tautan."

msgid "Enable or disable this announcement"
msgstr "Aktifkan atau nonaktifkan pengumuman ini"

msgid ""
"Announcement will automatically stop displaying after this date/time. Leave "
"blank for no expiry."
msgstr ""
"Pengumuman akan secara otomatis berhenti ditampilkan setelah tanggal/waktu "
"ini. Biarkan kosong untuk tidak berakhir."

msgid "Lower number = higher priority (displayed first)"
msgstr ""
"Angka yang lebih rendah = prioritas lebih tinggi (ditampilkan lebih dulu)"

msgid "Visibility rules for conditional display"
msgstr "Aturan visibilitas untuk tampilan kondisional"

msgid "Translations for announcement content"
msgstr "Terjemahan untuk konten pengumuman"

msgid "Announcement"
msgstr "Pengumuman"

msgid "Edit Announcement"
msgstr "Ubah Pengumuman"

msgid "Add Announcement"
msgstr "Tambahkan Pengumuman"

msgid "Please correct the errors below."
msgstr "Silakan perbaiki kesalahan di bawah ini."

msgid "Announcement headline — supports bold, italic, and font color."
msgstr "Judul pengumuman — mendukung tebal, miring, dan warna font."

msgid "Body"
msgstr "Isi"

msgid "Optional detail text shown in the modal popup."
msgstr "Teks detail opsional yang ditampilkan dalam popup modal."

msgid "Link Type"
msgstr "Jenis Tautan"

msgid "Button Text"
msgstr "Teks Tombol"

msgid "E.g. \\"
msgstr "Contoh. "

msgid "Show Modal"
msgstr "Tampilkan Modal"

msgid "Open details in a popup instead of navigating."
msgstr "Buka detail dalam popup alih-alih menavigasi."

msgid "Optional"
msgstr "Opsional"

msgid ""
"Image for the modal popup. Shown when a visitor clicks the announcement."
msgstr ""
"Gambar untuk popup modal. Ditampilkan ketika pengunjung mengklik pengumuman."

msgid "Display Mode"
msgstr "Mode Tampilan"

msgid "Overlay Opacity"
msgstr "Ketebalan Lapisan"

msgid "0 = transparent, 1 = opaque"
msgstr "0 = transparan, 1 = tidak transparan"

msgid "Enabled"
msgstr "Diaktifkan"

msgid "Priority"
msgstr "Prioritas"

msgid "Lower = shown first"
msgstr "Lebih rendah = ditampilkan terlebih dahulu"

msgid "Expires At"
msgstr "Berakhir Pada"

msgid "Leave blank for no expiry."
msgstr "Biarkan kosong jika tidak ada tanggal kedaluwarsa."

msgid "Created"
msgstr "Dibuat"

msgid "Updated"
msgstr "Diperbarui"

msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "Lanjut"

msgid ""
"Restrict when this announcement is shown. Leave empty to show to everyone."
msgstr ""
"Batasi kapan pengumuman ini ditampilkan. Biarkan kosong untuk menampilkan ke "
"semua orang."

msgid "Hold Ctrl / Cmd to select multiple."
msgstr "Tahan Ctrl / Cmd untuk memilih beberapa."

msgid "Save"
msgstr "Simpan"

msgid "Save & Continue"
msgstr "Simpan & Lanjutkan"

msgid "Save & Add Another"
msgstr "Simpan & Tambahkan Lainnya"

msgid "Delete"
msgstr "Hapus"

msgid "Manage store announcements displayed in headers and footers"
msgstr "Kelola pengumuman toko yang ditampilkan di header dan footer"

msgid "All"
msgstr "Semua"

msgid "Disabled"
msgstr "Dinonaktifkan"

msgid "Search announcements..."
msgstr "Cari pengumuman..."

msgid "announcements"
msgstr "pengumuman"

msgid "Previous"
msgstr "Sebelumnya"

msgid "of"
msgstr "dari"

msgid "Next"
msgstr "Berikutnya"

msgid "No Announcements Found"
msgstr "Tidak Ada Pengumuman Ditemukan"

msgid "No announcements match your search query."
msgstr "Tidak ada pengumuman yang cocok dengan query pencarian Anda."

msgid ""
"Create your first announcement to display in your store's header or footer."
msgstr ""
"Buat pengumuman pertama Anda untuk ditampilkan di header atau footer toko "
"Anda."

msgid "Create Announcement"
msgstr "Buat Pengumuman"

msgid "Opens modal on click"
msgstr "Buka modal saat diklik"

msgid "Modal"
msgstr "Modal"

msgid "Direct link on click"
msgstr "Tautan langsung saat diklik"

msgid "Direct Link"
msgstr "Tautan Langsung"

msgid "Last updated"
msgstr "Terakhir Diperbarui"

msgid "ago"
msgstr "yang lalu"

msgid "Expires"
msgstr "Berakhir"

msgid "Has Image"
msgstr "Mempunyai Gambar"

msgid "Edit"
msgstr "Edit"
